cc.acquized.itembuilder.api

Class ItemBuilder.Unsafe

  • java.lang.Object
    • cc.acquized.itembuilder.api.ItemBuilder.Unsafe
  • Enclosing class:
    ItemBuilder

    public class ItemBuilder.Unsafe
extends Object
    This Methods are unsafe and should not be used when you don't know what they do. These methods can cause a corruption of the Players Inventory File when it contains a invalid Item and causes so that the PLayer can no longer join the World with the corrupted Inventory File.
    Since:
    1.5
    Author:
    Acquized
